snippet.title: Warriors: Rise to Glory! Trailer
snippet.description:
"Warriors: Rise to Glory!" A new game coming to Steam "Early-Access" on Q4 2017.
Check out our Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/582330/Warriors_Rise_to_Glory/

Warriors: Rise to Glory is a Turn-Based Battle game with RPG elements. During your journey you will encounter various enemies with different skill sets. Fight epic BOSSES and get stronger with each battle by improving your warrior and purchasing epic armors and weapons!
